'''''Omicron 1 & 2''''' were a pair of [[Alliance to Restore the Republic/Legends|Rebel Alliance]] [[Beta-class ETR-3 escort transport|''Beta''-class ETR-3 escort transports]] colluding with the [[Airam sector/Legends|Airam]] pirates at a [[Goff Platform]] in the [[Goff system/Legends|Goff system]]. ''Omicron 1'' was crewed by regular Alliance personnel, while ''Omicron 2'' carried officers.

During the attack by the [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Imperial]] forces of [[Task Force Vengeance]], the ETRs of ''Omicron'' group concentrated their counterattack on the Interdictor ''[[Compellor]]''.

